clientSide.stubs

Class TableStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.stubs.TableStub

  • public class TableStub
extends java.lang.Object
    Stub to the table stub It instantiates a remote reference to the table stub. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
